C

Charmander - class Charmander.
A Charmander is a Pokemon that maintains information about its level, speed, strength, special, defense, total health, current health, experience points, name, attack names, and it's pokemon number.
Charmander(int) - Constructor for class Charmander
Creates a Charmander with all attributes based on the Charmander's level specified by x.
